        <mxCell id="hGi304kJ1s9SQkjNComQ-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional Requirements:" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="210" x="70" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hGi304kJ1s9SQkjNComQ-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. User must be able to login / register to the e-commerce platform.&lt;div&gt;2. User must be able to search the products.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Product Catalog Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Cart Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;5. User must be able to track the status of order.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;6. Check out service&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="460" x="100" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hGi304kJ1s9SQkjNComQ-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Non Functional Requirements:" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="190" x="100" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hGi304kJ1s9SQkjNComQ-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. System must be able to handle about 1-1.5 million daily active users.&lt;div&gt;2. Availability and Consistency depends on the system&#39;s functionality:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- System must be available while viewing the products.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- System must be consistent during the payment.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. System must be scalable to handle huge traffic during big billion sales.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Latency ~ 400ms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="180" width="500" x="100" y="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hGi304kJ1s9SQkjNComQ-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Database Schema Design:&lt;div&gt;1. User DB : stores user details&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Product DB : for storing the product details&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Orders DB: for storing the orders details along with their status&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="450" x="100" y="350" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
